{"article_id":"oAMZxlf4HxoUXGDP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A potential rift is growing within the GOP over the future of Attorney General Jeff Sessions .","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"`` The president is entitled to an attorney general","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"he has faith in ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"somebody","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"that 's qualified for the job , ''","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"( R-SC )","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"told reporters .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"While Graham may back the president 's frustration ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"others are stressing caution .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"`` The idea","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"that Jeff Sessions might be fired","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"because he 's not a political hack","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"is a very , very bad idea , ''","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"warned Sen. Ben Sasse","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"( R-NE ) .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"`` There may be a few isolated voices","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"that the president ought to fire him now ;","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"I can tell you as a body ,","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"we 're saying","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"please do n't , ''","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"echoed Sen. Jeff Flake","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"( R-AZ )","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"during an interview with NBC 's `` Meet the Press . '' In a recent interview with Fox News , President Donald Trump hammered Sessions over his decision","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"to recuse himself from the Russia investigation .","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"`` Jeff Sessions never took control of the Justice Department .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"It 's sort of an incredible thing , ''","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"`` He took the job","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"and then he said ,","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"' I 'm going to recuse myself . '","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"I said ,","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"'What kind of a man is this ? ''","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"Trump questioned .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"In a rare move , Sessions responded to the president 's jabs ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` The actions of the Department of Justice will not be improperly influenced by political considerations . ''","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"This comes","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"after former Trump attorney Michael Cohen pleaded guilty to breaking campaign finance laws .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"He also accused the president of ordering him to do so .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Cohen was caught during special counsel Robert Mueller 's investigation into possible collusion between the Trump campaign and Russian officials .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Democrats are n't talking impeachment yet ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"but","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"should they take the House in November","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"they 'll begin their own investigations .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"`` We should be investigating all of those things","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"- the interference of the Russians in our investigations , what we can do","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"to make sure","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"that ca n't happen again ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"who in the United States aided and abetted that , ''","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"said Rep. Jerry Nadler","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"( D-NY ) .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"According to a report from Axios ' Jonathan Swan ,","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"Republicans are gearing up for a wide range of investigations ,","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"even circulating a spreadsheet with a list of possible inquiries","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"including the president 's tax returns and The White House staff 's use of personal email .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Legal scholar Alan Dershowitz says","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"the case for impeachment simply is n't there .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"`` I fully understand","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"why so many people want , hope","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that President Trump has committed crimes and impeachable offenses ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"but the evidence is n't there , ''","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"he told ABC 's `` This Week . ''","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"And more legal news","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"surrounding the President ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Trump 's CFO Allen Weisselberg and National Inquirer publisher David Pecker , were also given immunity","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"to testify to Southern District of New York 's case","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"surrounding Michael Cohen .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"Still , the president 's supporters point out","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"none of it has anything to do with Russia collusion .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":143,"left":0,"right":142,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":113,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":1,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":108,"right":111,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":78,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":75,"right":77,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":73,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":76,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":76,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":79,"right":106,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":9,"right":10,